<p itemprop="description"><a class="seo_link brand-hover" href="https://pinpai.smzdm.com/1673/" data-brandid="1673" target="_blank">惠普</a><a class="seo_link brand-hover" href="https://pinpai.smzdm.com/1673/" data-brandid="1673" target="_blank">HP</a>8570W minipcie无线<a class="seo_link" href="https://www.smzdm.com/fenlei/wangka/" target="_blank">网卡</a>接口改装m.2网卡Intel9260AC</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a785ok75/pic_2/' target='_blank'><img alt="惠普HP8570W minipcie无线网卡接口改装m.2网卡Inte" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202009/18/5f64d71c001579948.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">拆开惠普HP8570W ，<a class="seo_link" href="https://www.smzdm.com/fenlei/zhuban/" target="_blank">主板</a>上有3个白色的连接器，一个用于转msata盘，一个是wwan接口用于转4G模块，还有一个是装着无线网卡的minipcie接口。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a785ok75/pic_3/' target='_blank'><img alt="惠普HP8570W minipcie无线网卡接口改装m.2网卡Inte" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202009/18/5f64d72a88cd81347.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">经过测试，wwan接口不能用于转接m.2网卡Intel9260AC，所以就是无线网卡的minipcie接口了。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a785ok75/pic_4/' target='_blank'><img alt="惠普HP8570W minipcie无线网卡接口改装m.2网卡Inte" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202009/18/5f64d730b09b05575.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">minipcie接口的空间只有半高尺寸，得用这款有排线延长线的转卡将m.2网卡Intel9260AC放置到其他地方。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a785ok75/pic_5/' target='_blank'><img alt="惠普HP8570W minipcie无线网卡接口改装m.2网卡Inte" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202009/18/5f64d7479d1009310.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">安装<a class="seo_link brand-hover" href="https://pinpai.smzdm.com/1699/" data-brandid="1699" target="_blank">intel</a>9260AC网卡到转卡的m.2接口上，使用100mm长的排线连接转卡的2部分，转卡的minipcie安装到主板上，转卡的m.2连带intel9260AC网卡隐藏到左上角的红圈下，天线延长线对接好原装天线，皱纹胶贴好排线，整体效果看起来干脆利落。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a785ok75/pic_6/' target='_blank'><img alt="惠普HP8570W minipcie无线网卡接口改装m.2网卡Inte" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202009/18/5f64d7545a5853083.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">这个改装方法也适用于wifi6网卡ax200，另外，更新官网的最新版本bios则不需要刷白名单。</p><p itemprop="description">开机查看改装的效果。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a785ok75/pic_7/' target='_blank'><img alt="惠普HP8570W minipcie无线网卡接口改装m.2网卡Inte" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202009/18/5f64d75d76cb51503.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p>
